title: Matthew Drew (The EP)
description:
Matthew Drew is a young singer/songwriter from Maine. He has been compared to Ben Folds, Dave Matthews, John Mayer and has performed in over a dozen different bands, ranging from jazz to punk to rock and everything in between. This EP Sampler features six songs that have been recorded over a period of three years. 

The first two songs were recorded with his band, November 42nd.

1. The Awakening
2. Wonderful Find
3. You
4. Pictures
5. Stripped From The Hook (home demo)
6. Question One (home demo)
